title: Nike x Sacai
description: A classic gets distorted in the Nike x Sacai Hoodie. Designer Chitose Abe remixes a staple by combining pieces of an athletics tracksuit with the Sunburst jacket. The result is a hybrid homage to Nike's past, paying it forward with comfortable fleece and zip storage.
material: Zip hand pocket on the left side can store a card or key.
detailed:
ICONS OF DISTORTION.
A classic gets distorted in the Nike x Sacai Hoodie. Designer Chitose Abe remixes a staple by combining pieces of an athletics tracksuit with the Sunburst jacket. The result is a hybrid homage to Nike's past, paying it forward with comfortable fleece and zip storage.
Designed For MovementBy bringing together different apparel elements from Nike's past, Chitose Abe creates a layered piece that flows when in motion. The resulting look showcases the beauty of movement.
Spliced IconicThis hybrid design brings together 2 classics—the 1976 Athletics Chain Link Tracksuit and the 1976 Auburn Sunburst Jacket. The mix of running and lifestyle icons features a dual zip closure so you can go with full coverage or leave it half-way unzipped from the top or bottom.
Personalised CoverageA lined hood provides coverage from the elements. A drawcord lets you personalise the fit.
BenefitsFleece fabric is soft, comfortable and warm.Split kangaroo pocket stores small items and helps keep your hands warm.Zip hand pocket on the left side can store a card or key.
Product DetailsRibbedStepped hem, neckline and cuffNods to Nike's heritage include a 1972 Swoosh design sunburst and pin-wheel graphicBody: 70% cotton/30% polyester. Panels: 100% polyester. Insets: 97% cotton/3% elastane. Hood Lining: 70% cotton/30% polyester.Machine washImportedColour Shown: Canyon Gold/ObsidianStyle: CD6303-711Country/Region of Origin: Vietnam
Nike x SacaiIn an ambitious celebration of motion, Sacai and Nike team up to drop a collection overflowing with style and creativity. Remixed designs receive freshly updated perspectives as Sacai lead designer Chitose Abe delivers all-new icons of distortion. Shifting the focus from technical performance, Sacai has rearranged the status quo to champion the beauty of movement over all else.
